        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " the porch was as. long as the house was broad). This curious statement answers to what we read in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1Kings 6:3",
        "children": []
