        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). It is out of the question that the porch should be of this height in itself. And almost as much out of the question that, if it could be so, this should be the only place to mention it by word or. description. There can be no doubt that the text is here slightly corrupt, and perhaps it is a further indication of this that, while the parallel contains ",
        "children": []
